e encyclopedia jump to navigation search for other people named mark burnett see mark burnett disambiguation mark burnett burnett in  born   july  age  london england occupation television producer executive producer author spouses roma downey m  two sons children james and cameron burnett mark burnett born  july  is a television and film producer and author and since december  president of mgm television and digital group he has won ten emmy awards five producers guild of america awards seven critics choice television awards and six peoples choice awards currently burnett is the executive producer of five network television showsspecials and two cable shows the voice nbc survivor cbs shark tank abc steve harvey’s funderdome abc and jamie foxxs beat shazam fox signed vh and lucha underground the el rey network in  burnett had timeslot winning shows on six nights out of seven in december  burnett was named president of mgm television and digital group adding numerous scripted television shows including fargo fxthe handmaid’s tale hulu vikings history and teen wolf mtv scripted shows that can be expected in the coming months include condor directv and get shorty epix burnett additionally produced the cable miniseries the bible and ad the bible continues as well as the feature films son of god little boy and woodlawn contents  early life  early career  productions  personal life  awards honors and affiliations  awards  nominations and wins  published works  see also  references  external links early lifeedit burnett was born on  july  in london the only child of archie and jean burnett both ford motors factory workers and was raised in dagenham essex his father was a roman catholic and his mother was a presbyterian although it is not known in which denomination he was raised aged  he enlisted in the british army and became a section commander in the parachute regiment from – he served with the rd battalion parachute regiment in c company and saw action during the falklands war early careeredit in october  burnett emigrated to the united states where his friend nick hill who had emigrated from the uk several years earlier was working as a nanny and chauffeur hill knew of an open position for a livein nanny with the jaeger family in affluent beverly hills despite having no experience as a nanny burnett went on the interview the jaegers realizing the advantage of having a nanny and security at the same time hired him after a year of working for the jaegers he moved on to another family in the beach city of malibu california taking care of two boys for  a week he was eventually given a position in the insurance office owned by burt the father of the two boys two years later burnett rented a portion of a fence at venice beach in los angeles and sold tshirts for  each during weekends realizing he made more money selling tshirts he left his insurance job in  burnett and four others joined a french adventure competition the raid gauloises afterward burnett saw a business opportunity in holding similar competitions he purchased the format rights and brought a similar competition ecochallenge to america ecochallenge launched burnetts career as a television producer productionsedit burnett is best known for producing the hit reality show survivor which premiered in the summer of  and was the most watched summer series since sonny and cher survivor was named the number  reality series of all time by entertainment weekly in  in  nbc premiered the apprentice a reality television series in which contestants competed for a job under real estate magnate and future president donald trump the apprentice spawned numerous licensed international versions of the show burnett has produced several other television franchises including are you smarter than a th grader shark tank and the voice he has maintained a strong presence in award show franchises having produced the mtv movie awards – the annual peoples choice awards – the spike video game awards    and the  primetime emmy awardscitation needed burnett has produced more than  hours of television programming which regularly airs in more than  countries past shows include celebrity apprentice nbc bully beatdown combat missions the contender the contender asia expedition africa expedition impossible howd you get so rich martha stewart my dad is better than your dad on the lot a collaboration with steven spielberg the restaurant rock star sarah palins alaska stars earn stripes starmaker toughest cowboy and wedding day as well as his ongoing productions burnett and his wife actress roma downey produced the bible a hour history channel drama based upon stories of the bible the bible became the no  new series on cable tv in  and was the no  series in canada spain and portugal in total with subsequent airings the bible was seen by more than  million viewers after the success of the bible burnett and downey started developing more faithbased scripted series ad the bible continues premiered on nbc on easter sunday  and the dovekeepers miniseries aired on cbs in spring  in october  nbc announced that it has reached a deal with burnett and richard bransons virgin galactic to produce a television series on which contestants will compete to win a spaceflight aboard spaceshiptwo the series will be titled space race although it is currently undeterminable when the show will begin airing in september  mgm acquired a  percent interest in one three media and lightworkers media both operated by burnett and his wife the two companies will be consolidated into a new film and television company united artists media group burnett is uamgs ceo and downey is president of lightworkers media in december  burnett was named president of mgm television and digital group signing a fiveyear deal burnetts appointment was set up to occur simultaneously with the closing of mgms acquisition of the remaining  percent of hearsts burnetts and roma downey‘s interests in united artists media group uamg which will be absorbed under the mgm television group umbrella mgm television will now have numerous unscripted and scripted television shows airing on network and cable or in production including the voice nbc survivor cbs shark tank abc beyond the tank abc celebrity apprentice nbc fargo fxvikings history teen wolf mtv  questions abc the peoples choice awards cbs lucha underground el rey network and americas greatest makers intelturner in  burnett produced the film benhur a film adaptation of the novel benhur a tale of the christ the film was a box office flop personal lifeedit in january  burnett began dating downey in november  while the two were vacationing with their children in zihuatanejo mexico he proposed to her they wed on  april  in their malibu home the ceremony was officiated by downeys former co star della reese burnett is an evangelical christian downey and him produced the bible miniseries and are now coowners of united artists media group together with mgm and hearst in addition to their producing projects the couple is heavily involved with philanthropic organizations operation smile and compassion international in  they announced a fundraising plan called cradle of christianity that aims to raise  million to help iraqi and syrian christians and other minorities displaced by isil survive that upcoming winter burnett was previously married to dianne j burnett née valentine they have two sons james and cameron the couple filed for legal separation in september  and a judgment for legal separation was granted in december  they later divorced in when awards honors and affiliationsedit in  time called burnett one of the most influential people in the world today burnett was also named philanthropist of the year by the reality cares foundation he has won both brandweeks marketer of the year award the prestigious rose d’or frapa format award the brandon tartikoff legacy award and the norman lear award from the producers guild of america burnett served for two years on the board of directors for the british academy of film and television arts in november  burnett was elected into the broadcast  cable hall of fame and in  it was announced that he would be honoured with a star on the hollywood walk of fame on  july  burnett received a star at  hollywood blvd in june  burnett was elected into the producers guild of america council board of delegates and currently serves on the producers council he is an ambassador for operation smile in  the tenhour miniseries the bible received the parents television council  seal of approval shark tank the voice and survivor were all nominated for critics choice awards at which the voice won for best reality series  competition the three shows were nominated for the television critics association awards at which shark tank won for outstanding achievement in reality programming in  the voice shark tank and the bible were nominated for primetime emmy awards the voice won for outstanding reality – competition program the voice and shark tank were nominated at the  critics’ choice television awards at which shark tank won for best reality series in  burnett and his wife roma downey were recipients of the antidefamation leagues entertainment industry award awardsedit special awards  brandweek marketer of the year award  reality cares foundation philanthropist of the year  brandon tartikoff legacy award  time magazine time   most influential people in the world today  rose d’or frapa format award  producers guild of america norman lear award  hollywood walk of fame star excellence in television  producers guild of america lifetime achievement award in television  tv guide magazine producer of the year  the dove foundation recognition of son of god  antidefamation league entertainment award nominations and winsedit year award category nominated work result  sports emmy award best program achievement ecochallenge morocco won  publicists guild of america maxwell weinberg publicists showmansh